raph.  The last two graphs are implicitly defined functions which requ
ire the Maple command " }{TEXT 297 0 "" }{TEXT 298 15 "implicitplot3d \+
" }{TEXT 299 0 "" }{TEXT -1 29 "which is part of the package " }{TEXT 
